## Description {#details}

Contains all scheduling relevant data for an instruction.

A ScheduleData either represents a single instruction or a member of an instruction bundle (= a group of instructions which is combined into a vector instruction).

Definition at line 3890 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/slpvectorizer-cpp">SLPVectorizer.cpp</a>.

### ControlDependencies {#acd94a2da39e146df17d9be2c9c0f0dfd}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>SmallVector&lt;ScheduleData &#42;, 4&gt; llvm::slpvectorizer::BoUpSLP::ScheduleData::ControlDependencies</>}>
List of instructions which this instruction could be control dependent on.

Allowing such nodes to be scheduled below this one could introduce a runtime fault which didn&#39;t exist in the original program. ex: this is a load or udiv following a readonly call which inf loops

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/slpvectorizer-cpp/#l04035">4035</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/slpvectorizer-cpp">SLPVectorizer.cpp</a>.

### Dependencies {#af346642fa514c45ca29171ad68501363}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="int llvm::slpvectorizer::BoUpSLP::ScheduleData::Dependencies = InvalidDeps">
The number of dependencies.

Constitutes of the number of users of the instruction plus the number of dependent memory instructions (if any). This value is calculated on demand. If InvalidDeps, the number of dependencies is not calculated yet.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/slpvectorizer-cpp/#l04048">4048</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/slpvectorizer-cpp">SLPVectorizer.cpp</a>.
